{"type":"text","timestamp":1784650212377,"sessionID":"ses_07a91b76bffeQVZz6UB7PapKuO","part":{"id":"prt_f8570f707001p2CwtWnql90DeT","messageID":"msg_f8570c374001ieeOYdHuun9tY9","sessionID":"ses_07a91b76bffeQVZz6UB7PapKuO","type":"text","text":"The prompt is the canonical `fanout-run.cjs` full-lineage payload. This session is already the first-level detached `cli-opencode` executor, so it must not recursively invoke another same-kind `opencode run`; the YAML manager will dispatch fresh LEAF `deep-review` iterations while retaining command ownership of state and reduction.","time":{"start":1784650200839,"end":1784650212371},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_03f0e82d94f6d585016a5f99d8c9fc8191bc65f7410e12cc5d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
