{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784654331464,"sessionID":"ses_07a91b76bffeQVZz6UB7PapKuO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_EcoYSvI2YKkQM0zfl02BD1WQ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Audit operator API parity","prompt":"Execute one deep-review LEAF iteration using `.opencode/specs/sk-design/017-remediation-program-review/review/lineages/gpt-56-sol-high/prompts/iteration-008.md`. Follow it verbatim. This is iteration 8 only. Do not dispatch subagents. Return concise verified status after writing required lineage-local outputs.","subagent_type":"deep-review","command":"/deep:review :auto"},"output":"<task id=\"ses_07a5887adffe0RmOGxu3tBXZ4u\" state=\"completed\">\n<task_result>\n## Review Iteration 8 Complete\n\n- **Focus:** Maintainability—operator/API parity\n- **New findings:** 2 total — P0: 0, P1: 2, P2: 0\n- **Findings:** malformed options silently select defaults; clean-checkout status throws `ENOENT`\n- **newFindingsRatio:** 0.25\n- **Verdict:** CONDITIONAL\n- **Verification:** 13/13 focused tests passed; state/delta records parse and match exactly; final verdict line verified\n- **Dimensions:** All covered; iterations 9–10 remain by forced-depth policy\n- **Next focus:** Adversarial validation of parity and performance claims\n- **Files written:** `iteration-008.md`, `iter-008.jsonl`, state append, strategy update\n- **Status:** `complete`\n</task_result>\n</task>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_07a91b76bffeQVZz6UB7PapKuO","sessionId":"ses_07a5887adffe0RmOGxu3tBXZ4u","model":{"modelID":"gpt-5.6-sol","providerID":"openai"},"truncated":false},"title":"Audit operator API parity","time":{"start":1784653773119,"end":1784654331450}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0661554fc00f7d2b016a5fa7c22c5c8191bdabfbbc5e9cca6f"}},"id":"prt_f85a77843001IwJinISCsgBjAb","sessionID":"ses_07a91b76bffeQVZz6UB7PapKuO","messageID":"msg_f85a73e500012ivYwyMmcVXA5G"}}
