"Initial discovery (iteration summary)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"dimensions\": [\n        \"correctness\"\n      ],\n      \"mergedFindingIds\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"findingId\": \"P1-004\",\n      \"severity\": \"P1\",\n      \"title\": \"The database module README sends every operator command to the removed _db tree\",\n      \"file\": \".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/lib/database/README.md\",\n      \"line\": 75,\n      \"description\": \"All five supported operator examples invoke absent styles/_db/operator.mjs while the executable lives at styles/lib/database/operator.mjs.\",\n      \"findingClass\": \"matrix/evidence\",\n      \"deltaStatus\": null,\n      \"scopeProof\": \"Manifest-scoped sweep plus direct path checks proved five stale command examples, no compatibility executable, and the relocated operator present.\",\n      \"affectedSurfaceHints\": [\n        \"database operator onboarding\",\n        \"status/build/cutover/rollback/repair commands\",\n        \"adapter-mode documentation\",\n        \"follow-on path edits\"\n      ],\n      \"contentHash\": \"sha256:4f8ce8f7707a3903ca99232419b9c1a42f590f842819bc55f38c6850694f0b66\",\n      \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n      \"firstSeen\": 4,\n      \"lastSeen\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"transitions\": [\n        {\n          \"iteration\": 4,\n          \"from\": null,\n          \"to\": \"P1\",\n          \"reason\": \"Initial discovery (iteration summary)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"dimensions\": [\n        \"correctness\"\n      ],\n      \"mergedFindingIds\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"findingId\": \"P1-005\",\n      \"severity\": \"P1\",\n      \"title\": \"Generated packet graphs still encode pre-rewrite status and pre-restructure paths\",\n      \"file\": \".opencode/specs/sk-design/012-style-database-and-interface-commands/008-interface-command-rewrite/graph-metadata.json\",\n      \"line\": 42,\n      \"description\": \"The 012 graph remains in_progress despite IMPLEMENTED authority, while 001/004 graphs expose removed _db files as key files and entities.\",\n      \"findingClass\": \"cross-consumer\",\n      \"deltaStatus\": null,\n      \"scopeProof\": \"Manifest-listed metadata parsed successfully; direct status/path comparison found stale current-state graph fields across 012, 001, and 004.\",\n      \"affectedSurfaceHints\": [\n        \"Spec Kit resume status\",\n        \"code-graph entity navigation\",\n        \"memory indexing\",\n        \"generated-metadata refresh\",\n        \"packet dependency discovery\"\n      ],\n      \"contentHash\": \"sha256:a5590af0fc7b364239e037d7e2c9e81056163d4a4b4cc4cf9109b49fd560975b\",\n      \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n      \"firstSeen\": 4,\n      \"lastSeen\": 4,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"transitions\": [\n        {\n          \"iteration\": 4,\n          \"from\": null,\n          \"to\": \"P1\",\n          \"reason\": \"Initial discovery (iteration summary)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"dimensions\": [\n        \"correctness\"\n      ],\n      \"mergedFindingIds\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"findingId\": \"P1-006\",\n      \"severity\": \"P1\",\n      \"title\": \"Post-query generation drift is mislabeled as no-fit in every corpus consumer\",\n      \"file\": \".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/corpus/comparison-lane.mjs\",\n      \"line\": 503,\n      \"description\": \"All four consumers detect a post-query generation mismatch but pass no-fit into builders that already model generation-mismatch as requery-required.\",\n      \"findingClass\": \"cross-consumer\",\n      \"deltaStatus\": null,\n      \"scopeProof\": \"All four manifest-listed production classifiers repeat the branch; 76/76 focused tests show the current no-fit behavior is stable.\",\n      \"affectedSurfaceHints\": [\n        \"audit comparison fallback\",\n        \"foundations relationship fallback\",\n        \"interface exemplar fallback\",\n        \"motion evidence fallback\",\n        \"stale-generation requery orchestration\"\n      ],\n      \"contentHash\": \"sha256:54c9b28c7c7df7e2a62a55b1b90ec639a833e2b1a651a9419dae19ce12bfccf4\",\n      \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n      \"firstSeen\": 6,\n      \"lastSeen\": 7,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"transitions\": [\n        {\n          \"iteration\": 6,\n          \"from\": null,\n          \"to\": \"P1\",\n          \"reason\": \"Initial discovery (iteration summary)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"dimensions\": [\n        \"correctness\"\n      ],\n      \"mergedFindingIds\": []\n    },\n    {\n      \"findingId\": \"P1-009\",\n      \"severity\": \"P1\",\n      \"title\": \"The 10/10 shadow result does not prove full facade DTO parity\",\n      \"file\": \".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/lib/engine/persistent-adapter.mjs\",\n      \"line\": 115,\n      \"description\": \"Shadow parity compares a projection and tolerates score values, ranking mode, content hash, and generation hash, so 10/10 cannot prove full facade DTO parity.\",\n      \"findingClass\": \"matrix/evidence\",\n      \"deltaStatus\": null,\n      \"scopeProof\": \"The manifest has one shadow fixture assertion and a nine-scenario persistent golden oracle, but no committed ten-query legacy/persistent full-DTO artifact.\",\n      \"affectedSurfaceHints\": [\n        \"shadow comparator\",\n        \"facade DTO\",\n        \"ten-query evidence\",\n        \"cutover parity gate\"\n      ],\n      \"contentHash\": \"sha256:1266283898ea8cf75f46b9740c2f1b6233f605808034fd9b582e709205ebd378\",\n      \"dimension\": \"correctness\",\n      \"firstSeen\": 9,\n      \"lastSeen\": 9,\n      \"status\": \"active\",\n      \"transitions\": [\n        {\n          \"iteration\": 9,\n          \"from\": null,\n          \"to\": \"P1\",\n          \"reason\": \"Initial discovery (iteration summary)\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"dimensions\": [\n        \"correctness\"\n      ],\n      \"mergedFindingIds\": []\n